    drawTank is a class that creates tanks in the Play Menu

    GameOverMenu opens a JFrame diplays the Game Over Screen and prompts the user(s) to play again

    GameScreen is a class that controls all in-game sequences

    MainMenu

    Player is a class that holds all information about a player's current status in the game
    PlayMenu
    PlayMenu is a class that allows users to name their tanks, and select a tank color
    playMusic
    playMusic is a class that helps load the Tanks theme music into the game

    Shoot is a class that holds and updates information regarding a tank projectile's current x and y coordinates
